{"tid":1244133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[防守珠羅紀] 歡迎大家分享戰略","createTime":"2019-06-19T18:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T18:42:58.000Z","uid":61160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0447ee164e933cfeb902bcbeb3a472b22ad2aa9d","tid":1244133,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"珠羅紀其實好易打，基本上佢地係全攻裝備。冇防守能力，講既係速度<br />\n佢地既用處只有一個，將人群攻散後退後，後面軍裝上黎將防線推前。<br />\n從而打散。<br />\n<br />\n基本上珠羅紀只會向前跑，後面會有一隻拉住佢免得前面個隻珠羅紀比人捉走。<br />\n<br />\n防守戰略:<br />\n1. 當珠羅紀進攻時，立即放下大量令人唔敢向前跑既圓球體，例如波子。佢自己仆街唔係你打佢，所以唔關你事。佢地步履維艱時攻擊力大減<br />\n<br />\n歡迎分享<br />\n<br />\n利申 jurassic World fans"},{"pid":"effc9f324ec3b968648d822a8f01c2eb59fd2027","tid":1244133,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"歡迎分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e074b8873c7a08c70249ea5d84268fcf185259c","tid":1244133,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"歡迎分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7b6fe2bcabcc0a1f114b4f80acf86b9f15d3fc","tid":1244133,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"歡迎分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a25f93653dd276b930063ddc0e6e57e84e1be64","tid":1244133,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"歡迎分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bf10764349c4ce66f81a4d426ba766122c3a9b","tid":1244133,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:25:10.000Z","msg":"歡迎分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e42a4d54d4d26101fa87605df29487428c9e0f4","tid":1244133,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:25:53.000Z","msg":"